snippet.title: Amber Heard accused of pocketing $7M divorce settlement
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp is accusing ex-wife Amber Heard of pocketing the massive $7M settlement from their divorce and repeatedly lying about giving it all to charity, DailyMail.com can exclusively reveal.

Original Story: https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9118921/Johnny-Depp-accuses-Amber-Heard-taking-7M-settlement-lying-giving-charity.html
